{
  "chapter": 32,
  "chapter_summary": "小方决定离开盗窟，阳光暗中警告他注意严正刚的左手暗藏玄机。小方先发制人击败了埋伏在门后的宋老夫子，随后面对严正刚的左手杀人术。小方识破严正刚利用宋老夫子做\"第三只手\"前后夹击的诡计，以同样手法反制，声称自己也有\"第三只手\"，实则是阳光提供了情报。严正刚出手时宋老夫子已被制服，小方趁机脱身。随后小方遇见鹰记商号总管朱云，朱云先以恭敬态度与小方交手，随后突然亮出真功夫。朱云揭露阳光手上戴着三十三种剧毒淬成的毒戒，握手时已将毒刺刺入小方掌心，中毒者半个时辰内必死。朱云用夺命七星针和青铜剑发动致命一击，小方因信心动摇、情绪沮丧而难以闪避，生死悬于一线。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你也是来为我饯行的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你知不知道他们准备用什么来为你饯行？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "用我的人头？还是用我的血？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "你要说的我都知道，可是随便他们要用什么，我都不在乎。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "反正我已决心要走了。随便用什么法子走都一样。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 25
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "好了，你走吧！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你从这道门走，第一个要为你饯行的是严正刚，你要特别注意他的手。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "我知道。我会特别注意他的左手。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "不但要注意他的左手，还要注意他另外一只手。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 45
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "另外一只手？右手？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "不是右手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yan_zheng_gang",
      "text": "你准备用什么替我饯行？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_zheng_gang",
      "speaker_name": "严正刚",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "用我的左手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_zheng_gang",
      "speaker_name": "严正刚",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "这里是盗窟，入了盗窟，就像是入了地狱，想离开只有再世为人，你要走，我就只有杀了你，用我的左手杀你。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_zheng_gang",
      "speaker_name": "严正刚",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我从来不用武器，我这只手就是杀人的武器！江湖中善用左手的人，出手绝没有比我更快，所以你一定要特别注意。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yan_zheng_gang",
      "text": "我见过你出手，我会注意的。可是我不懂，你既然要杀我，为什么又要提醒我注意？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_zheng_gang",
      "speaker_name": "严正刚",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "因为我要你死得心服口服。我要你死而无怨。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 83
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yan_zheng_gang",
      "text": "严正刚果然人如其名，刚直公正，绝不肯做欺人的事，所以你如果偶尔做一次，谁也不会怀疑的。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yan_zheng_gang",
      "text": "如果我真的全神贯注，注意你的左手，今天我就死定了。幸好我还没有忘记柳分分。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_zheng_gang",
      "speaker_name": "严正刚",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "柳分分？她怎么样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yan_zheng_gang",
      "text": "连她都没有怀疑你，连她都上了你的当，何况我这个初出道的小伙子？你能做宋老夫子的第三只手，当然也可以用他的手做你的第三只手，用第三只手来杀我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yan_zheng_gang",
      "text": "那时我死得虽然心不服口不服，心里就算有一肚子怨气，也发不出来了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_zheng_gang",
      "speaker_name": "严正刚",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "想不到你居然还不太笨。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yan_zheng_gang",
      "text": "还有件事你一定也想不到。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_zheng_gang",
      "speaker_name": "严正刚",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yan_zheng_gang",
      "text": "我另外也有只手。第三只手。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_zheng_gang",
      "speaker_name": "严正刚",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你也有第三只手？我怎么看不见？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yan_zheng_gang",
      "text": "你当然看不见，你永远都看不见的。但是你却绝对不能不信。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_zheng_gang",
      "speaker_name": "严正刚",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yan_zheng_gang",
      "text": "因为你的第三只手，现在已经被我的第三只手绑起来了。如果你不信，不妨自己去看看。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "朱云",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "晚辈朱云，恭请方大侠赐招。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_zhu_yun",
      "text": "我不是大侠，你也不是我的晚辈，你不必太客气。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "朱云",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "方大侠一定会认为晚辈还未尽全力，还不该放手的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "朱云",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "晚辈不愿血战，只因为晚辈已不忍再与方大侠缠斗下去了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_zhu_yun",
      "text": "你不忍？为什么不忍？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "朱云",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "因为大侠已中了奇毒，已经绝对活不到半个时辰了。如果晚辈再缠斗二十招，方大侠的毒性一发作，就必死无救了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_zhu_yun",
      "text": "我中了毒？你看得出我中了毒？是什么时候中的毒？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "朱云",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "就在片刻之前。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_zhu_yun",
      "text": "卜鹰给我喝的酒中有毒？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "朱云",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "没有，酒里绝对没有毒。他要杀你，也不必用毒酒。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_zhu_yun",
      "text": "毒不在酒，在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "朱云",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "在手上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "朱云",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "谁的手？你刚才握过谁的手？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "朱云",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "其实你应该想得到的，她也是要为你饯行的人，第一个为你饯行的就是她，只不过她用的方法和我们不同而已！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_zhu_yun",
      "text": "有什么不同？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "朱云",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "她的方法远比我们温和。但是也远比我们有效。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_zhu_yun",
      "text": "她用的是什么法子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "朱云",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你们最近常在一起，你应该看得见她手上一直戴着个戒指。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "朱云",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "可是她戴的那个戒指不同。那个戒指虽然只有几钱重，却远比几百两黄金更珍贵！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_zhu_yun",
      "text": "为什么？是不是因为它的手工特别精细？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "朱云",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "不是！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_zhu_yun",
      "text": "是为了什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "朱云",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "是因为戒指上的毒。是用三十三种剧毒淬成的，先将这三十三种剧毒淬入黄金，再打成这么样一个戒指，戒指上有一根刺，比针尖还细的刺，刺入你的皮肤时，你连一点感觉都没有，可是半个时辰内，你已必死无救。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "朱云",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "本来我们都已经把你当作朋友，如果你不走，这里绝对没有人会伤害你，阳光更不会。不幸现在我们已经不是朋友了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 311
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_zhu_yun",
      "text": "我知道你想说什么。不是朋友，就是仇敌，所以她才会用这种方法对付我，你们对付仇敌本来就是不择手段的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_zhu_yun",
      "text": "她先把严正刚和宋老夫子的杀招告诉我，为的就是要稳住我，要我对她完全信任，她才能在我不知不觉中把毒刺刺入我的掌心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_zhu_yun",
      "text": "可是你为什么要把这件事告诉我呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_zhu_yun",
      "text": "蝮蛇螫手，壮士断腕。你是不是要我斩断自己这只手？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "朱云",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_yun",
      "speaker_name": "朱云",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "但是你不妨先看看你自己这只手，看看你手上是不是已经有了个好像被毒蜂螫过的伤口，如果伤口还没有发黑，也许你还有救。",
      "tone": "认真",
